# Nombre del paquete (minúsculas-separado-con-guiones)
name: plymouth-theme-bardinux-text

# Autor 
author: Enrique Hernández Bello <quique@osl.ull.es>

# Priority
priority: optional

# Section
section: x11

# Descripción corta
shortdesc: "graphical boot animation and logger - bardinux-text theme"

# Descipción larga, las lineas han de estar separadas por "\n "
longdesc: "Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process\n (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical\n boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.\n .\n This package contains the default bardinux-text theme used when no\n support for a graphical theme is found on your system."

# Versión del paquete
version: 4.0.1

# Cambios en esta versión
changes:
